{"word":"Peter","slug":"peter","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Peter</b> - the apostle<p/>General References to<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=18'>Mat 4:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=41'>Joh 1:41</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=3&verse=16'>Mar 3:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=16'>Mat 16:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=5&verse=37'>Mar 5:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=9&verse=2'>Mar 9:2</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=24'>Mat 17:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=18&verse=21'>Mat 18:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=19&verse=27'>Mat 19:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=8'>Luk 22:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=22&verse=31'>Luk 22:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=13&verse=6'>Joh 13:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=37'>Mat 26:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=58'>Mat 26:58</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=69'>Mat 26:69</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=24&verse=12'>Luk 24:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=24&verse=34'>Luk 24:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=21&verse=3'>Joh 21:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=21&verse=15'>Joh 21:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=15'>Act 1:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=2&verse=14'>Act 2:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=3&verse=1'>Act 3:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=4&verse=8'>Act 4:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=5&verse=3'>Act 5:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=5&verse=29'>Act 5:29</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=8&verse=14'>Act 8:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=8&verse=20'>Act 8:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=9&verse=32'>Act 9:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=9&verse=40'>Act 9:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=10&verse=9'>Act 10:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=11&verse=2'>Act 11:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=3'>Act 12:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=7'>Act 15:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=1&verse=12'>1Co 1:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=9&verse=5'>1Co 9:5</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=1&verse=18'>Gal 1:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=2&verse=11'>Gal 2:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=1&verse=1'>1Pe 1:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=5&verse=1'>1Pe 5:1</a><p/>-- <b>\"The Reed Changed to a Rock\"</b><p/>Naturally impulsive<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=14&verse=28'>Mat 14:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=4'>Mat 17:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=21&verse=7'>Joh 21:7</a><p/>Tenderhearted and affectionate<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=75'>Mat 26:75</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=13&verse=9'>Joh 13:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=21&verse=15'>Joh 21:15-17</a><p/>Full of strange contradictions, - at times presumptuous<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=22'>Mat 16:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=13&verse=8'>Joh 13:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=18&verse=10'>Joh 18:10</a><p/>other times timid and cowardly<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=14&verse=30'>Mat 14:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=69'>Mat 26:69-72</a><p/>Self-sacrificing<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=18'>Mr 1:18</a><p/>yet inclined to be self-seeking<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=19&verse=27'>Mt 19:27</a><p/>Gifted with Spiritual insight<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=68'>Joh 6:68</a><p/>yet slow to apprehend the deeper truths<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=15&verse=15'>Mat 15:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=15&verse=16'>Mat 15:16</a><p/>Made two great confession of his faith in Christ<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=16'>Mat 16:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=69'>Joh 6:69</a><p/>and also the most cowardly denial<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=67'>Mr 14:67-71</a><p/>-- <b>Seven Steps in his Fall</b><p/>1--Conceit<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=33'>Mt 26:33</a><p/>2--Ease<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=40'>Mt 26:40</a><p/>3--Rashness<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=18&verse=10'>Joh 18:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=18&verse=11'>Joh 18:11</a><p/>4--Following afar off<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=58'>Mt 26:58</a><p/>5--Evil associations<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=18&verse=18'>Joh 18:18</a><p/>6--Open Denial<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=18&verse=25'>Joh 18:25</a><p/>7--Blasphemy<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=70'>Mar 14:70</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=71'>Mar 14:71</a><p/>-- <b>After Pentecostal Baptism</b> of the Spirit, he became a \"rock\"<p/>fulfilling the prophecy of Christ<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=42'>Joh 1:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=18'>Mat 16:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=8'>Act 1:8</a><p/>Was courageous and immovable<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=4&verse=19'>Act 4:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=4&verse=20'>Act 4:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=5&verse=28'>Act 5:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=5&verse=29'>Act 5:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=5&verse=40'>Act 5:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=5&verse=40'>Act 5:40</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Miracles of, MIRACLES"}]}